Package: pedometrics
Version: 0.11.1
Date: 2022-05-25
Title: Miscellaneous Pedometric Tools
Description: An R implementation of some useful tools employed in the field of pedometrics. Some of
    these tools use the popular geostatistical packages geoR and georob. From time to time, these
    suggested packages may be archived (temporarily removed from CRAN) due to issues with their own
    dependencies. Formerly available versions can be obtained from the CRAN archive
    <https://cran.r-project.org/src/contrib/Archive/>.
